=== DOCUMENTATION FOR TARGET: DEV1G ===

<target_short_dscr>:
Device 2G5
------------------------------
<target_public_text>:
The device operates as an interface between the TAXI bus and SGMII / USXGMII macro supporting data rates of 10M, 100M, 1000Mbps, and 2.5 Gbps. The device includes PCS, MAC and rate adaption logic.
