<field_public_text>:
Block Lock Hysteresis Enable. This is a configuration to control the an_sync_status of USXGMII ANEG w.r.t. block lock. Setting this bit will set an_sync_status to fail link_timer duration after the block_lock is set to false. If the bit is cleared, loss of block lock will set an_sync_status to fail causing an autoneg restart as is mentioned in USXGMII Specification.
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
1: an_sync_status is cleared after link timer duration of block_lock = 0
0: an_sync_status is cleared immediately after block_lock = 0
